{"tid":1095900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【賤種法官下場】重慶法院前院長遭賊人劫殺","createTime":"2019-04-07T10:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T11:46:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"359c2c1d77a2fb9516adf7fbc7ba8f4a99e7ab41","tid":1095900,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190407/large/1554630703_3286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190407%2Flarge%2F1554630703_3286.jpg&h=dd77630a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重慶市第二中院表示，該院前副院長譚智華被殺，警方調查後指事件涉及入屋盜竊，譚智華在反抗時被殺，但未有透露具體的案情。不過，很多網民都說事有蹊蹺，懷疑事件背後應該有內情。<br />\n內地媒體今日下午報道譚智華遇害的消息，報道只有67字，只透露譚志華遇害的消息，及警方已經介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n公開資料顯示，現年55歲的譚志華是土家族人，來自重慶石柱，1994年取得律師資格，2006年獲委任為黔江區法院院長，及後升任重慶市二中院副院長，2016年底他被市人大免去副院長職務，當局未公佈他的新職位，但重慶二中院的微博在去年底報道一個會議時，指當時譚志華仍在法院任職，職位是「審判委員會專職委員」。<br />\n<br />\n「我認為這可能不是簡單的入室搶劫，從仇家查起吧！」不少內地網民都認為「新聞越短，越有內情」，懷疑譚志華被殺不會只是入屋盜竊。有網民認為：「盜竊是煙幕，殺人是目的！」「副院長的家能輕易入室？現在小區安全已經到了這個地步啦？」「是因為知道得太多了！」"},{"pid":"5a17a3ec11daa2ec2d72473112a968b688c36e96","tid":1095900,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34a418d20fea1bcdfaf89393a7b65fa8603b1310","tid":1095900,"uid":170335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:56:24.000Z","msg":"睇黎係個好官"},{"pid":"1ae2dc4741dec3d59334a4cec9e8bacecbe297aa","tid":1095900,"uid":201482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"15feb28d39a1e97b1c8941288aad163649a09f05","tid":1095900,"uid":46729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:59:07.000Z","msg":"點解賤種？"},{"pid":"88b22042c17c624dfcf83de010a0a5e3083afa7c","tid":1095900,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:08:07.000Z","msg":"買錯邊落錯注既下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629031e7d77bca334d01392cdb31e0f538df5dc1","tid":1095900,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34a418d20fea1bcdfaf89393a7b65fa8603b1310","tid":1095900,"uid":170335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:56:24.000Z","msg":"睇黎係個好官"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:41:43.000Z","msg":"支那無官係無辜。  應該得罪其他勢力"},{"pid":"b594fa1a0edff3c9787c9a3cd7ba82e23919304f","tid":1095900,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:46:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xKPjQciPrXI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxKPjQciPrXI&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=8945c9e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xKPjQciPrXI</a><br />\n拍定片先可以遲幾年先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}